Normally you would use lifecycle observers by using LifeData,
but it is not necessary to use it here, because if the
individual fragments get destroyed the data should not be saved.
Only if the game is over by loosing 5 hearts this should happen.
And you also can't interact more with the UI than selecting the correct answers.


